snippet.title: Graphing Quadratic Functions - Example 1
snippet.description:
Thanks to all of you who support me on Patreon. You da real mvps!   $1 per month helps!! :)  https://www.patreon.com/patrickjmt !! 
Graphing Quadratic Functions - Example 1. In this video, I outline a little recipe of things to examine when graphing a quadratic function by hand.  I then proceed to do one example of graphing a quadratic function.
  For more free math videos, visit http://JustMathTutoring.com
